Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.08,0:00:05.33,Sunburst,,0,0,0,,That's the last entry…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.33,0:00:08.20,Sunburst,,0,0,0,,Starswirl's final words before he vanished!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.20,0:00:11.04,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,All those legendary ponies were real too?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.04,0:00:13.60,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,And then none of them were ever heard from again?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.60,0:00:16.24,Twilight,,0,0,0,,They used their magic to open a portal to limbo…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.50,0:00:21.62,Twilight,,0,0,0,,We need to find items that are connected to the Pillars in some way.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.24,0:00:23.54,Twilight,,0,0,0,,We've brought you back!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.54,0:00:26.52,Starswirl,,0,0,0,,You cannot bring only the pillars back!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.22,0:01:18.46,PonyOfShadows,,0,0,0,,Your pitiful attempt to imprison me has failed, Starswirl!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.99,0:01:24.85,Starswirl,,0,0,0,,You must return us to limbo. It's the only way to stop him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.86,0:01:26.89,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I only figured out how to bring you back.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.04,0:01:29.64,Sunburst,,0,0,0,,Working on it…No table of contents…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.85,0:01:31.84,PonyOfShadows,,0,0,0,,Allow me to assist.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.40,0:01:44.08,PonyOfShadows,,0,0,0,,There.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.52,0:01:46.65,PonyOfShadows,,0,0,0,,Without the power of Ponhenge,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.65,0:01:49.55,PonyOfShadows,,0,0,0,,your banishing spell is useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.68,0:01:51.36,Starswirl,,0,0,0,,You have studied my writings.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.36,0:01:53.36,Starswirl,,0,0,0,,Surely you have some other plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.63,0:01:56.52,Twilight,,0,0,0,,No. I just wanted to save you, I didn't think…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.52,0:01:57.55,PonyOfShadows,,0,0,0,,Don't fret.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.55,0:02:01.88,PonyOfShadows,,0,0,0,,When I extinguish the light and hope of this miserable world…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.22,0:02:04.30,PonyOfShadows,,0,0,0,,You won't remember any of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.07,0:02:05.92,Twilight,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.51,0:02:12.06,PonyOfShadows,,0,0,0,,This one is almost as strong as you, Starswirl.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.06,0:02:16.14,PonyOfShadows,,0,0,0,,But even in my weakened state, she cannot stop the might of shadows!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.62,0:02:22.92,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Lucky for her, she's not alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.31,0:02:29.12,Starswirl,,0,0,0,,Know this, fiend.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.12,0:02:33.39,Starswirl,,0,0,0,,We will not rest until we find a way to return you to limbo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.76,0:02:35.76,PonyOfShadows,,0,0,0,,Never.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.00,0:02:38.40,PonyOfShadows,,0,0,0,,Your days of glory are through, Starswirl.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.80,0:02:41.36,PonyOfShadows,,0,0,0,,Now my dark power will reign,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.36,0:02:44.52,PonyOfShadows,,0,0,0,,and you six will bow to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.83,0:02:49.76,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Where'd he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.25,0:02:53.45,Somnambula,,0,0,0,,That is a riddle we must unravel. And quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.53,0:02:55.45,Meadowbrook,,0,0,0,,How long have we been gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.45,0:02:57.45,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Over a thousand years.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.57,0:03:02.80,Starswirl,,0,0,0,,Then my spell worked — before it was meddled with
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.80,0:03:05.66,Starswirl,,0,0,0,,and the realm has been at peace for a millennia!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.66,0:03:07.20,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Weeeeell…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.20,0:03:11.34,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,we did have to save everypony from Nightmare Moon, and Discord, and Chrysalis, and King Sombra, and Lord Tirek,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.34,0:03:15.00,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,and there was that one time when Starlight traveled through time and almost destroyed life as we know it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.47,0:03:17.44,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,But that's all in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.96,0:03:19.98,FlashMagnus,,0,0,0,,If you are truly this accomplished,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.98,0:03:23.66,FlashMagnus,,0,0,0,,we will stop the Pony of Shadows twice as fast together.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.66,0:03:25.21,Starswirl,,0,0,0,,We shall see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.21,0:03:28.83,Starswirl,,0,0,0,,It is an easy thing to say you have saved the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.83,0:03:30.83,Starswirl,,0,0,0,,It is quite another to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.07,0:03:33.96,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Oh, we've saved the world, beardo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.14,0:03:35.58,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,And we can do it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.80,0:03:37.42,Starswirl,,0,0,0,,Be that as it may.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.42,0:03:41.12,Starswirl,,0,0,0,,The problem of locating the Pony of Shadows remains.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.12,0:03:43.12,Starswirl,,0,0,0,,And this land is vast.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.40,0:03:45.16,Rarity,,0,0,0,,It sounds like you need a map.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.52,0:03:47.96,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Luckily, we have just the thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.53,0:03:52.67,Starswirl,,0,0,0,,Something about this magic seems familiar…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.44,0:03:59.13,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Did you know he could do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.13,0:04:01.34,Twilight,,0,0,0,,He's Starswirl! He can do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.25,0:04:05.45,Starswirl,,0,0,0,,This map and, indeed, this very castle
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.45,0:04:10.04,Starswirl,,0,0,0,,are grown from the seed we planted over a thousand years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.04,0:04:11.20,Rockhoof,,0,0,0,,Then it did work!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.48,0:04:12.35,Sunburst,,0,0,0,,What worked?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.49,0:04:15.92,Somnambula,,0,0,0,,Each of us infused a crystal seed with our magic
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.92,0:04:19.08,Somnambula,,0,0,0,,in hopes that it would grow into a force for good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.08,0:04:23.98,Mistmane,,0,0,0,,We wanted to leave something to protect the realm in our absence, but
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.98,0:04:28.00,Mistmane,,0,0,0,,we never dreamed our gift would become so powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.20,0:04:30.65,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Y'all mean the elements came from you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.44,0:04:37.53,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,You know, the sparkly crystal things that grow from the tree of harmony and represent each of us?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.04,0:04:39.07,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Laughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.07,0:04:39.92,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Honesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.92,0:04:41.07,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Generosity.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.07,0:04:42.01,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Loyalty.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.01,0:04:43.10,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Kindness.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.10,0:04:44.96,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,And magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.40,0:04:49.84,Somnambula,,0,0,0,,They are reflections of our own elements of hope,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.84,0:04:50.80,Somnambula,,0,0,0,,strength,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.80,0:04:51.84,Somnambula,,0,0,0,,beauty,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.84,0:04:52.80,Somnambula,,0,0,0,,bravery,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.80,0:04:53.68,Somnambula,,0,0,0,,healing,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.68,0:04:55.02,Somnambula,,0,0,0,,and sorcery.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.13,0:05:03.21,Meadowbrook,,0,0,0,,We had no idea our small seed would bloom into the living spirit of the land.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.21,0:05:07.47,Meadowbrook,,0,0,0,,I am glad our mantles have passed to such capable ponies.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.47,0:05:09.08,Starswirl,,0,0,0,,More importantly,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.08,0:05:13.61,Starswirl,,0,0,0,,we no longer need Ponhenge to send our foe back to limbo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.61,0:05:17.92,Starswirl,,0,0,0,,We can use the stored magic in this "Tree of Harmony."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.92,0:05:20.86,Twilight,,0,0,0,,But… Doesn't a banishing spell take a lot of power?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.86,0:05:23.12,Twilight,,0,0,0,,We'd have to sacrifice the elements for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.11,0:05:25.87,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,They'd be gone… Forever?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.22,0:05:30.04,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Starswirl…I don't think the Tree can survive without the elements.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.04,0:05:32.73,Twilight,,0,0,0,,If it dies, Equestria will suffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.73,0:05:37.15,Starswirl,,0,0,0,,If the Pony of Shadows has his way, your land will not exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.15,0:05:40.46,Starswirl,,0,0,0,,So unless you have a better idea…?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.70,0:05:51.23,Starswirl,,0,0,0,,Our foe will seek dark places from which to draw power.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.23,0:05:55.98,Starswirl,,0,0,0,,I will prepare my spell, so that we may strike as soon as you find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.57,0:05:58.11,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,What are we waiting for?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.11,0:05:59.77,FlashMagnus,,0,0,0,,I like your spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.43,0:06:07.47,Spike,,0,0,0,,What about this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.88,0:06:11.55,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Sea Pony etiquette isn't going to help right now, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.98,0:06:16.01,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Twilight? Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.38,0:06:21.00,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I just unleashed ultimate evil and doomed Equestria because I was obsessed with meeting my idol.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.00,0:06:22.38,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Why wouldn't I be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.72,0:06:25.44,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,You didn't know that was gonna happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.88,0:06:27.93,Twilight,,0,0,0,,But I should have listened to you and left things alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.93,0:06:30.86,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Now the elements of harmony will be lost to fix my mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.26,0:06:32.86,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Maybe there's another way…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.21,0:06:35.36,Spike,,0,0,0,,If there is, Twilight will find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.55,0:06:40.83,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Portal gate… Portal keys… Portal spells… Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.83,0:06:45.79,Twilight,,0,0,0,,If the Pillars can hold open the gateway to limbo, a powerful pony can do the banishing spell herself!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.79,0:06:47.10,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Do you know what this means?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.11,0:06:49.95,Spike,,0,0,0,,I can stop carrying books?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.44,0:06:52.52,Twilight,,0,0,0,,The Pillars don't have to leave Equestria!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.52,0:06:55.85,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Even though we'll lose the elements, we'll have the ponies that created them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.85,0:06:58.20,Twilight,,0,0,0,,And the Pony of Shadows will be banished for good!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.84,0:07:00.20,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,That's great…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.84,0:07:06.36,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,But I was thinking of another way that maybe doesn't involve "banishing" at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.80,0:07:09.82,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Starswirl knew what he was doing when he cast that spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.82,0:07:11.26,Twilight,,0,0,0,,If I can make it even better…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.26,0:07:14.17,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Maybe he'll see I take magic as seriously as he does.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.20,0:07:24.09,Rockhoof,,0,0,0,,It seems the dark places Starswirl indicated on the map have changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.75,0:07:28.62,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I bet the Pony of Shadows woulda loved the Ghastly Caverns
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.62,0:07:32.81,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,before 1000 years of erosion turned it into the Ghastly Gorge…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.81,0:07:36.43,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,The "Appleloosian Wastes" sure sounded dark and desolate.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.83,0:07:40.09,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Who knew they would become such a popular square dancing destination?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.09,0:07:44.40,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,And I get how this part of Equestria used to be cast in eternal night
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.40,0:07:46.97,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,where the Pony of Shadows could draw power
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.97,0:07:50.16,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,and wreak havoc while ponies were powerless to stop him,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.16,0:07:50.84,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,but…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.32,0:07:52.54,PinkiePieBright,,0,0,0,,…it's kinda made a comeback.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.91,0:07:54.92,PinkiePieBright,,0,0,0,,Did I mention it's really bright?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.48,0:08:03.60,Starswirl,,0,0,0,,It seems there are fewer dark corners in the realm these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.60,0:08:05.60,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Isn't that a good thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.60,0:08:09.47,FlashMagnus,,0,0,0,,True. The Pony of Shadows will have a hard time regaining power.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.47,0:08:12.24,FlashMagnus,,0,0,0,,When he rears his head, we'll be ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.31,0:08:16.48,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Isn't there some way to banish him without losing all of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.39,0:08:18.84,Meadowbrook,,0,0,0,,I wish there were.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.23,0:08:22.62,Meadowbrook,,0,0,0,,But to save our home, we are willing to leave it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.00,0:08:24.88,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I don't think you'll have to!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.88,0:08:26.33,Twilight,,0,0,0,,My spell isn't finished yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.33,0:08:30.59,Twilight,,0,0,0,,but I think we can send The Pony of Shadows to limbo without all of you having to go as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.77,0:08:36.08,Starswirl,,0,0,0,,While I appreciate your enthusiasm, Twilight,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.08,0:08:40.35,Starswirl,,0,0,0,,this is hardly the time to take risks on half-baked spells.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.71,0:08:43.66,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Begging your pardon, Mr. The Bearded.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.01,0:08:46.70,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,But Twilight doesn't do anything half-way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.97,0:08:49.63,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Especially not magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.63,0:08:54.32,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Seriously! She got her wings by finishing one of your spells.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.32,0:08:58.00,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I think you'll find her work is worth reading before you dismiss it out of hoof!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.53,0:09:03.60,Meadowbrook,,0,0,0,,While it is an unconventional approach, I believe it could work.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.21,0:09:07.45,Starswirl,,0,0,0,,I suppose there is a chance…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.80,0:09:10.88,Sunburst,,0,0,0,,But we still have no idea where to find the villain.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.80,0:09:21.60,Spike,,0,0,0,,Maybe we should try there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.68,0:09:29.32,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,The Hollow Shades.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.32,0:09:31.92,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I think a branch of the Apple family lives there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.92,0:09:33.92,Sunburst,,0,0,0,,They'd have to be pretty distant.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.92,0:09:36.64,Sunburst,,0,0,0,,The Hollow Shades was abandoned eons ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.60,0:09:43.08,Rarity,,0,0,0,,That's odd. The only time the map's called all of us to one place was Starlight's village.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.08,0:09:45.64,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,So it's like a super-villain tracker!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.53,0:09:47.46,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,No offense.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.79,0:09:52.05,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Do you think the map could be trying to tell us where the Pony of Shadows is?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.11,0:09:56.96,Starswirl,,0,0,0,,Tree of Harmony acting to protect the light of the realm…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.38,0:09:59.12,Starswirl,,0,0,0,,Yes, a good thought, Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.00,0:10:02.79,Starswirl,,0,0,0,,I will make my notes on this spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.79,0:10:04.36,Starswirl,,0,0,0,,Ready yourselves for battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.16,0:10:10.32,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,I know I'm not as experienced as all of you, but is banishment really the only option?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.32,0:10:12.32,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,I mean, it's been a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.32,0:10:15.33,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Maybe the Pony of Shadows is ready to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.75,0:10:19.00,Starswirl,,0,0,0,,I doubt we can save our homeland with a conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.32,0:10:20.71,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,But we could try.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.71,0:10:24.24,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Starlight, I'm sure Starswirl and the others did try.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.56,0:10:27.68,Starswirl,,0,0,0,,The Pony of Shadows was not interested in reconciliation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.68,0:10:29.68,Starswirl,,0,0,0,,Once a villain, always a villain.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.36,0:10:31.68,Starswirl,,0,0,0,,Twilight, Sunburst,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.40,0:10:33.51,Starswirl,,0,0,0,,would you accompany me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.51,0:10:36.16,Starswirl,,0,0,0,,I wish to refine this spell for our use.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.28,0:10:40.34,Rockhoof,,0,0,0,,Come. We must prepare for the struggle ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.27,0:10:48.56,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,I know Starswirl is a great wizard, but this whole plan seems wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.06,0:10:51.89,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,The map's only ever sent us to solve friendship problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.21,0:10:57.06,Spike,,0,0,0,,Maybe so, but the Pony of Shadows doesn't really seem like the friendship type.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.51,0:11:00.05,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Honestly, we don't know anything about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.64,0:11:01.92,Spike,,0,0,0,,Nopony does.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.88,0:11:05.11,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,That's not entirely true.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.00,0:11:16.79,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,You all knew the Pony of Shadows before he became what he is now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.79,0:11:19.83,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,You must've been friends. So what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.06,0:11:23.30,Rockhoof,,0,0,0,,The tale of our rift is a sad one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.79,0:11:43.12,Rockhoof,,0,0,0,,Stygian was a pony like the rest of us,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.12,0:11:45.12,Rockhoof,,0,0,0,,though more scholar than hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.12,0:11:49.08,Rockhoof,,0,0,0,,He recognized our emerging world would need champions to defend it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.65,0:12:09.83,FlashMagnus,,0,0,0,,He may have gathered us together,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.83,0:12:15.16,FlashMagnus,,0,0,0,,but he, himself, was just an ordinary unicorn who soon grew jealous of our abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.95,0:12:19.44,Mistmane,,0,0,0,,He stole objects from each of us
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.68,0:12:23.16,Mistmane,,0,0,0,,artifacts to use in a spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.12,0:12:26.64,Meadowbrook,,0,0,0,,And we cast him out for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.90,0:12:32.18,Somnambula,,0,0,0,,We always thought he'd return and seek forgiveness…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.50,0:12:36.71,Somnambula,,0,0,0,,But when we saw him again, his heart was bent on revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.83,0:12:40.71,Somnambula,,0,0,0,,He dashed even my hope of saving him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.21,0:12:46.40,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,But why did he steal the artifacts from you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.63,0:12:50.82,Meadowbrook,,0,0,0,,No doubt it was an enchantment to take our powers for himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.60,0:12:59.90,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,That looks like a lot of work.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.90,0:13:03.86,Starswirl,,0,0,0,,It is what must be done, and it would be best if we were not disturbed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.82,0:13:08.71,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Starlight, but we can't stop to talk, the stakes are too high and we have to
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.71,0:13:11.00,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,banish Stygian to limbo. I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.91,0:13:12.34,Sunburst,,0,0,0,,Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.34,0:13:16.93,Starswirl,,0,0,0,,Stygian was the name the Pony of Shadows gave up when he turned to darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.16,0:13:19.73,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,And I'm just trying to figure out why.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.73,0:13:22.26,Starswirl,,0,0,0,,Envy. He wanted more power than he had,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.26,0:13:26.48,Starswirl,,0,0,0,,and that desire led him down a path from which there is no return.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.74,0:13:29.70,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,I know from experience that's not always true.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.70,0:13:33.46,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,When the map called you six to my village, it was for a friendship problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.46,0:13:35.36,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Are you sure this is different?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.36,0:13:36.18,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.18,0:13:39.49,Starswirl,,0,0,0,,Stygian wants to destroy all that is good in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.49,0:13:42.61,Starswirl,,0,0,0,,There's no way to befriend a pony like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.97,0:13:48.31,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,I guess I'm lucky your idol wasn't around when you decided to be my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.31,0:13:50.50,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,I might've been banished to limbo too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.37,0:14:03.34,Somnambula,,0,0,0,,I am glad we have the chance to see what has grown from our efforts so long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.34,0:14:06.24,Mistmane,,0,0,0,,It seems a shame to harm it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.24,0:14:07.87,Starswirl,,0,0,0,,A necessary sacrifice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.87,0:14:11.08,Starswirl,,0,0,0,,With the elements' power, we will bind the Pony of Shadows in limbo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.08,0:14:14.78,Starswirl,,0,0,0,,And thanks to Twilight, we will remain to watch over the realm ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.38,0:14:31.44,Rockhoof,,0,0,0,,How do we use them?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.44,0:14:32.48,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Well, you!..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.24,0:14:34.28,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.28,0:14:35.66,Rarity,,0,0,0,,They simply work for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.66,0:14:37.31,Starswirl,,0,0,0,,The elements are attuned to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.31,0:14:39.37,Starswirl,,0,0,0,,We must use their magic in pairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.37,0:14:40.62,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.62,0:14:43.42,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,We're used to banishing evil before breakfast.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.33,0:14:47.13,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,And it'll be an honor to save Equestria with y'all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.40,0:14:51.88,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,I really hope Twilight knows what she's doing…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.93,0:15:00.03,Sunburst,,0,0,0,,I don't remember reading anything that said the Hollow Shades was like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.85,0:15:05.76,Mistmane,,0,0,0,,The Pony of Shadows must have twisted it to his purposes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.45,0:15:11.13,Starswirl,,0,0,0,,Prepare yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.80,0:15:13.04,Starswirl,,0,0,0,,He is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.45,0:15:14.32,Starswirl,,0,0,0,,Stygian!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.32,0:15:16.43,Starswirl,,0,0,0,,Show yourself and face us!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.00,0:15:36.92,Sunburst,,0,0,0,,I definitely would have remembered reading about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.18,0:15:48.04,PonyOfShadows,,0,0,0,,Welcome to the Well of Shade!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.86,0:15:52.89,PonyOfShadows,,0,0,0,,When you turned your backs on me, I discovered this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.89,0:15:57.04,PonyOfShadows,,0,0,0,,The darkness spoke to me of a power beyond any I could imagine,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.04,0:15:58.97,PonyOfShadows,,0,0,0,,and I listened.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.97,0:16:01.52,PonyOfShadows,,0,0,0,,The shadow and I became one.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.52,0:16:04.84,PonyOfShadows,,0,0,0,,Soon all of the realm will be the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.84,0:16:08.75,PonyOfShadows,,0,0,0,,Then all ponies will feel the despair I did
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.75,0:16:10.75,PonyOfShadows,,0,0,0,,when you cast me out!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.75,0:16:12.60,Starswirl,,0,0,0,,We did what we had to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.60,0:16:15.72,Starswirl,,0,0,0,,You tried to steal our powers for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.27,0:16:18.48,PonyOfShadows,,0,0,0,,No. It was you who were selfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.94,0:16:21.77,PonyOfShadows,,0,0,0,,And now you will pay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.04,0:16:27.08,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Are you still sure this isn't a friendship problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.79,0:16:29.93,Starswirl,,0,0,0,,Ready? Open the portal…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.00,0:16:32.88,Starswirl,,0,0,0,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.88,0:16:48.62,PonyOfShadows,,0,0,0,,No! You will not trap me again!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.99,0:16:50.88,Starswirl,,0,0,0,,Twilight! Push him in!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.67,0:16:56.36,Twilight,,0,0,0,,There's…A pony in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.93,0:17:05.72,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Are you… Stygian?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.49,0:17:08.04,Stygian,,0,0,0,,I was, once.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.04,0:17:10.04,Stygian,,0,0,0,,Until my friends betrayed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.52,0:17:13.02,Twilight,,0,0,0,,But Starswirl says you betrayed them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.02,0:17:14.65,Twilight,,0,0,0,,You wanted their magic…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.65,0:17:16.89,Stygian,,0,0,0,,No! I wanted their respect.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.89,0:17:18.28,Stygian,,0,0,0,,I brought them together.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.28,0:17:21.88,Stygian,,0,0,0,,I planned strategy, and I read all I could about the beasts we faced…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.88,0:17:25.90,Stygian,,0,0,0,,But I didn't have magic or strength. So nopony ever noticed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.83,0:17:30.17,Stygian,,0,0,0,,I went to Ponhenge to make my own copies of the artifacts.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.17,0:17:32.68,Stygian,,0,0,0,,With them, I thought I could be a Pillar too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.68,0:17:34.67,Stygian,,0,0,0,,And stand by their side in battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.24,0:17:37.42,Stygian,,0,0,0,,I never wanted to steal their power.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.19,0:17:42.27,Stygian,,0,0,0,,But instead of sharing and letting me help… My friends threw me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.72,0:17:45.13,Stygian,,0,0,0,,So I became stronger than any of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.13,0:17:48.00,Stygian,,0,0,0,,The darkness welcomed me when nopony would
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.00,0:17:50.35,Stygian,,0,0,0,,and I will do what I must to protect it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.72,0:17:52.64,Twilight,,0,0,0,,This is all a misunderstanding!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.64,0:17:57.04,Twilight,,0,0,0,,If the Pillars knew how you felt, I'm sure they wouldn't have turned their backs on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.04,0:18:01.63,Twilight,,0,0,0,,The shadow isn't who you really are. Let me help you be Stygian again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.63,0:18:04.06,Stygian,,0,0,0,,Even if my friends did still care,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.06,0:18:06.96,Stygian,,0,0,0,,what makes you think you have the power to help me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.96,0:18:08.86,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Because it's what she does.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.86,0:18:12.06,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,I wasn't so different from you and Twilight helped me change.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.73,0:18:16.99,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,If there's one pony in Equestria that can save a friendship, it's her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.34,0:18:19.55,Stygian,,0,0,0,,I… I want to believe you…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.75,0:18:23.71,PonyOfShadows,,0,0,0,,But the darkness will not be stopped!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.31,0:18:33.13,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Fight the darkness, Stygian!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.13,0:18:35.48,Twilight,,0,0,0,,You don't need it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.48,0:18:37.66,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Revenge isn't what you want,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.66,0:18:38.89,Twilight,,0,0,0,,friendship is!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.04,0:18:42.04,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Twilight!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.47,0:18:49.10,Twilight,,0,0,0,,The shadow won't let go of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.10,0:18:52.09,Twilight,,0,0,0,,He wants to stop, but he can't do it alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.09,0:18:53.60,Starswirl,,0,0,0,,Then we must help him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.50,0:19:24.00,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Yeah! It felt sooooo good to do that again!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.00,0:19:25.96,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Friendship power rush!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.68,0:19:30.06,Rarity,,0,0,0,,The elements! They didn't disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.06,0:19:34.04,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Maybe because we used them for healing magic instead of banishing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.04,0:19:34.88,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.66,0:19:40.20,Starswirl,,0,0,0,,Long ago you needed our help, Stygian,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.20,0:19:43.52,Starswirl,,0,0,0,,but instead of listening, we turned our backs on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.52,0:19:45.48,Starswirl,,0,0,0,,Pride clouded my judgment…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.00,0:19:47.69,Starswirl,,0,0,0,,And I owe you an apology.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.28,0:19:52.48,Starswirl,,0,0,0,,Thank you for helping us see the errors of our ways, Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.48,0:19:56.41,Starswirl,,0,0,0,,It seems I never accounted for the magic of friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.99,0:19:58.70,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Swirlstar.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.99,0:20:00.49,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Starswirl!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.34,0:20:10.03,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,So apparently a conversation can save Equestria?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.40,0:20:16.24,Starswirl,,0,0,0,,Something tells me I will be making a lot of apologies today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.77,0:20:23.02,Starswirl,,0,0,0,,I simply cannot believe how tall you've gotten!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.02,0:20:26.40,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Well, it has been over a thousand years.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.40,0:20:29.18,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Will you stay here and teach magic once again?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.18,0:20:32.96,Celestia,,0,0,0,,My sister and I have such fond memories of your lessons.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.96,0:20:36.94,Luna,,0,0,0,,As long as you don't ask for those essays we owed you before you disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.88,0:20:40.62,Starswirl,,0,0,0,,I am not certain Canterlot is where I belong.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.21,0:20:47.04,Starswirl,,0,0,0,,The realm has grown and I believe I'll have a look around before I settle in any one place.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.04,0:20:50.22,Meadowbrook,,0,0,0,,And I long to see what has become of my home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.22,0:20:52.33,Mistmane,,0,0,0,,I believe we all do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.32,0:20:56.64,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Then I hope you will return to Canterlot on occasion
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.64,0:21:02.00,Celestia,,0,0,0,,and share the wisdom of your great experience with the next generation of ponies.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.00,0:21:05.07,Starswirl,,0,0,0,,We would be honored, but if it is wisdom you seek,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.07,0:21:07.53,Starswirl,,0,0,0,,look no further than your own pupil.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.53,0:21:12.41,Starswirl,,0,0,0,,She showed me that the power of friendship is a magical force indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.41,0:21:16.32,Starswirl,,0,0,0,,And that in turning away from others, you hurt yourself as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.98,0:21:24.33,Twilight,,0,0,0,,It's funny… I thought meeting my idol would give me all the answers I ever wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.33,0:21:27.00,Twilight,,0,0,0,,But instead, I forgot what I already knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.58,0:21:30.32,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Good thing I had a student of my own to remind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.96,0:21:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,SCHASTLIVY PONEC
